data.description: OPEN HOUSE: SUNDAY, APRIL 14TH 12-5PM!  Gorgeous 5-bedroom, 3.5 bath, immaculate home in Trophy Ridge!  This home is stunning from the moment you walk in! The spacious layout is perfect with high ceilings, beautiful laminate flooring, fresh paint (2023), new GE appliances (2023), new roof (2023), DuPont water softener and new plush carpet (2023). The gourmet kitchen is lovely with sprawling granite countertops, a convenient breakfast bar, and new stainless steel appliances. The dining room is elegant with a charming chandelier and tons of natural light.  Relax and unwind in the downstairs primary bedroom. The lovely sitting area has a gorgeous bay window and is the perfect retreat. The spacious en suite is luxurious with a huge spa-like garden tub, double vanities, separate shower, and large extended primary closet. This home offers so much space with 4 extra large bedrooms upstairs and a massive game room for entertaining.  Enjoy the tranquil backyard with a lovely covered patio, freshly mulched flowerbeds and an outdoor shed that coveys with the home. Residents enjoy neighborhood amenities to include a gorgeous swimming pool with covered awnings, an outdoor sports court, and a park with playground. This home is a great location with easy access to 1604/151, shopping, Lackland AFB and Sea World. Schedule a private showing today and start making memories in this beautiful home!
